{% section "Queue State" %}
<!-- live queue snapshot at session start -->

| Priority | Count | Next |
|---|---|---|
| 🔴 HIGH | `{{ queue_high }}` | `{{ next_task }}` |
| 🟡 MED | `{{ queue_med }}` | |
| 🟢 LOW | `{{ queue_low }}` | |
| ⚡ Running | `{{ queue_running }}` | |

```dataview
TABLE priority, assignee, skill_required, status
FROM "00-Inbox/tasks"
WHERE status = "claimed" OR status = "in-progress"
SORT priority ASC
LIMIT 5
```
{% endsection %}

{% section "Top Flags — Review Needed" %}
<!-- HIGH flags from REVIEW-INBOX promoted this session -->
<!-- Full list: 00-Inbox/AGENT-REVIEW-INBOX.md -->

```dataview
TABLE drop_type, from, priority, file.ctime AS "Flagged"
FROM "00-SHARED/00-Human-Inbox"
WHERE priority = "HIGH" AND read = false
SORT file.ctime DESC
LIMIT 8
```

*See [[00-SHARED/00-Human-Inbox/]] for full inbox.*
{% endsection %}

