{% section "Cross-Repo Connections" %}
<!-- CONNECTION-tagged observations spanning multiple repos in this investigation -->

```dataview
TABLE file.folder AS "Repo", file.ctime AS "Found"
FROM ""
WHERE type = "connection" AND contains(tags, "cross-repo")
  AND file.ctime >= date(today) - dur(7 day)
SORT file.ctime DESC
LIMIT 6
```
